<div id="desc">
<h3>New Boston Promotions Celebrates 20 Years in Business!</h3>
<p>
<br>
New Boston Promotions was founded by Mary Melodee Mena in 1988 to provide 
promotional products for clients of all sizes.  
Mary will help you use promotional products to deliver your message
to your target audience without waste.  Our products motivate, promote,
reward and sell&nbsp;&#8212;&nbsp;and they are desired and appreciated
when received.  Most of all, your message is kept and remembered 
&nbsp;&#8212;&nbsp;unlike traditional advertising.
</p>
</div>

<div id="main">
<h2>Client List</h2>

<h3>Comments from some satisfied customers:</h3>
<p>
&#8220;I&#8217;ve had the pleasure to work with Mary professionally for many years.   I was the Event Supervisor for the PBS program 
<i>Antiques Roadshow</i>. One of my tasks was to hire a supplier to provide shirts for the staff, crew and volunteers at the Roadshow 
taping events around the country. I invited Mary to give us an estimate. After sending great samples, advising us on the best fabric 
options and logo stitching techniques, her estimate beat the others hands down. So if you ever watch Antiques Roadshow, the polo 
shirts on all the &#8217;helpers&#8217; milling around the set in the background are Mary&#8217;s wares. Mary has earned my highest 
praise&nbsp;&#8212;&nbsp;please put at the top of the Mary Mena Fan Club!!&#8221;  <br><b>Beth Chambers-Fliss:</b> Event Supervisor, Antiques Roadshow
</p>

<p>
&#8220;Mary is one of the most accommodating, experienced, creative and trustworthy sources of promotional products I have ever worked 
with. I have worked with her for many years and have brought her with me to every place I have worked. Highly recommended!&#8221;<br>
<b>Sarah Blumenstock-Girell:</b> Freelance Print Production Manager
</p>

<p>
&#8220;Mary Melodee Mena offers exceptional service and results for premium promotional items used at any level event. She is very 
responsive and gets the job done.&#8221;<br>  
<b>Lynn Skinner:</b> Corporate Tradeshow Manager, Cognos Corp.
</p>

